snippet.textDisplay:
The Government Plan

Economic break down and profits have been lost,
For a poor man with a few shillings for certain items he is afraid of the cost,
On us they create a meek and simple plot,
If not death by genetic foods its viruses that causes our bones to rot,
After generations I've started to believe we are losing alot.

Education levels have no longer been noticed,
A certain time in the year they collect our votes quick,
A linear subtraction switch for each year we still repeat the cycle and know we are being tricked,
Vandalized,scandalized and brutalised we are being beated down with a mental whip.

Suffering in diverse places wars afar,
No stance taken because the ones who should protect us only worsen our scar,
And if you feel your too high for them they will put you behind the bar,
I speak of names of few,on a short and simple interview,
Christians failed to see muslims too,
That the truth is eating at us because what we should be surviving from we have to pay it as due,
And still we wonder and ponder whats there to do.

For years we have funded our own suffering and complain,
Unity is tearing us apart let me explain,
If we can never be at one we have only ourselves to blame,
I still feel like im being held back tied in chains,
Everyday is the same mind game,lame time frame,saddened rain,they gave us a way to be as a tip powerful by selling out for fame!

It is exactly as we think of it,
Before technology they played it all out in movies and books like its a myth,
The sequences of realistic disaster the mushroom bomb lit,
Hiroshima and Nagasaki have had their bit,
But i know many forget but many worry and all they do is sit,

Governments dont see that we dont wanna be in control of everything,
They have been lost and trying hard to take us to hell with their sin,
Look at my face im serious as the sun at 12 noon without grin,
Severely you wouldnt know that a cloned human was first teach to us in the centuries as a sim,
So many thoughts i bring,i dont fancy golds no not even a ring,
Because as i am i will return to the creator without a broken limb,

They made such thoughts on us as if we are their lambs,
As if we didn't know they told biggie and others years before the 9/11 bombs,
Knowing after all we will understand when we hear it play over in a 1996 song,
Now tell me after all this if you still dont understand the government plan?

snippet.textDisplay:
Boris, we need assistance from the Utility Companies, there could be so much more being done by them if they took the initative, but they too are looking out for themselves and as the PM, it may well mean that you will have to spur them on into playing a far more active role than they are.



Yes the mobile networks are an effective tool in this day and age to get the messages out to the public, but where else can they help. They can throw a life line to the Elderly in halving their bills during this out break It would be some measure in helping with the social distancing and would ease some of the worries and fears that they have in facing the next bill.



The same with Gas, and Electric, we have plenty of data on customers to really be able to make that difference to the vital minority of our society. The gaming industry could be doing more for their customers, rather than dragging them down into debt. They could be reducing their prices to make this far more affordable when youngsters are stuck in doors. Even if it's a marginal reduction at least it would help families and citizens cope a little easier.



Regarding Care Homes, this is just a thought, the military may well be useful in being able to supply all the necessitaries for those care homes if they could liaise with the "Care Home Managers" to get a comprehensive list of their weekly needs. Some elderly have been left to die as care workers have fled is what is being reported in certain countries. We do not want to get to that state, when we have the resources and the man power to deliver it.



Some of the stringent rules actually work against carers but how are you to know that. Aside from caring for myself, and immediate family there are friends and other extending families that are slipping through the net.

snippet.textDisplay:
I have, myself, full confidence that if all do their duty if nothing is neglected, and if the best
arrangements are made, as they are being made, we shall prove ourselves once again able to defend
our Island home, to ride out the storm of this infection, and to outlive the menace of this illness, if necessary for
years, if necessary alone. At any rate, that is what we are going to try to do. That is the resolve of Her
Majesty's Government-every man and women of them. That is the will of Parliament and the nation. The British
Islands and the WHO, linked together in their cause and in their need, will defend to the
death their citizens, aiding each other like good comrades to the utmost of their strength. Even
though large tracts of Europe and many old and famous States have fallen or may fall into the grip of
COVID 19 and all the unknown outcomes of it, we shall not flag or fail. We shall go on to the
the end, we shall equip the NHS, we shall fight this disease, we shall research with growing
confidence and growing strength in our laboratories, we shall save our people, whatever the cost may be, we
shall sanitize the pubs, we shall prevent people from going on the playgrounds, we shall decontaminate the parks and the
streets, we shall safe lives in our ICUs; we shall never surrender, and even if, which I do not for a moment
believe, this Island or a large part of it were subjugated and infectious, then our friends beyond the
seas, armed with science, would carry on the struggle, until, in God's good time,
the Medical World, with all its power and might, steps forth to the rescue and the liberation of this Nation- Stay Strong signed Winston C
